fr.sii.ogham.core.util

Class PriorizedList<P>

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.sii.ogham.core.util.PriorizedList<P>
  • Type Parameters:
    P - the type of priorized objects

    public class PriorizedList<P>
extends Object
    Helper class that registers objects with associated priority. Each registered object is then returned as list ordered by priority. The higher priority value comes first in the list.
